qoutes.text: Every year with you feels like a beautiful chapter of a fairy tale that I never want to end. Here’s to us and our incredible journey
From the moment we said ‘I do,’ my world has been colored with the hues of your love.
With each passing year, our love becomes deeper and more unbreakable. Here’s to forever, my dearest wife.
The years we’ve spent together are a testament to the strength of our love. I’m grateful for every moment by your side.
As we celebrate another year of togetherness, my heart is filled with gratitude for having you as my partner in life.

propose.text: I'm not sure what life could bring you. I'm not sure if dreams do come true. I'm not sure what love can do. But I'm sure about one thing. I love you
